---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Twistedline Games"
  description="Welcome To Twistedline Games Official website"
>
  <section class="remorses-background">
    <section class="mid-details">
      <section class="remorses-logo-wishlist">
        <img src="/Remorses_Text.png" alt="Remorses Logo" />
        <a
          href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2292160/Remorses/"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <button></button>
        </a>
      </section>

      <h1 class="headline" style="color: #e6e6e6;">Gameplay</h1>
      <p class="paragraph" style="color: #e6e6e6;">
        Remorses. Unveil the horror within a susceptible narrative set in a
        slowly paced, atmospheric and terrifying world. Survive the journey
        through sinister environments, where your sanity is tested. The very air
        you breathe becomes your lifeline, neglect it and face the consequences
        as an unsettling force toys with your mind.
      </p>

      <section class="youtube-sideText">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3Sjy3rb-GT8?si=V_UHU0rzFnbzTMiv"
          title="Remorses Trailer"
          allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share; xr-spatial-tracking"
          allowfullscreen
          class="remorses-trailer"
        >
        </iframe>

        <p class="paragraph" style="color: #e6e6e6;">
          Along your path, search for ingredients to craft, Investigate the
          unknown, solve puzzles, and craft your way to freedom while uncovering
          the horrifying truth that lurks within. Prepare for a sensory
          onslaught of visual, auditory, and logical puzzles.
        </p>
      </section>

      <h1 class="headline" style="color: #e6e6e6;">Story</h1>
      <p class="paragraph" style="color: #e6e6e6;">
        Step into the shoes of Jake, a seasoned investigator with curiosity for
        the supernatural. In his past, Jake wandered into the unknown, which
        yielded knowledge and understanding without peril. But this time, the
        game has changed. Whispers of witchcraft beckon him into a treacherous
        realm he never anticipated. Cornered and with no one to trust but
        himself, survival becomes the ultimate test. Can you navigate the
        perilous waters of the occult and emerge unscathed? Your fate awaits
        within the darkness.
      </p>

      <br />
      <br />
      <section class="remorses-snapshots">
        <img src="/Picture_1.png" alt="Picture_1" />
        <img src="/Picture_2.png" alt="Picture_2" />
        <img src="/Picture_3.png" alt="Picture_3" />
        <img src="/Picture_4.png" alt="Picture_4" />
        <img src="/Picture_5.jpg" alt="Picture_5" />
        <img src="/Picture_6.png" alt="Picture_6" />
        <img src="/Picture_7.png" alt="Picture_7" />
        <img src="/Picture_8.png" alt="Picture_8" />
        <img src="/Picture_9.png" alt="Picture_9" />
      </section>

      <h1 class="headline" style="color: #e6e6e6;">Characters</h1>
      <p class="paragraph" style="color: #e6e6e6;">
        The events of remorses not only move the story forward, but also reveal
        more about the character's past, present, and future.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>
